# Hoist the bundler-external native runtime deps to the workspace-root
# node_modules so the esbuild-bundled api/worker (`node dist/server.js`,
# `dist/worker.js`) can resolve them as bare specifiers. These packages are
# marked `external` in scripts/build-app.ts because they load native .node
# binaries and must come from node_modules at runtime (deployable-stack §5,
# Task 5). @huggingface/transformers is declared in packages/memory, so pnpm
# would otherwise only link it under packages/memory/node_modules — out of the
# /app/dist resolution path. Public-hoisting it (and its native deps) to the
# root keeps the bundle runnable as plain node from /app.
public-hoist-pattern[]=@huggingface/transformers
public-hoist-pattern[]=onnxruntime-node
public-hoist-pattern[]=sharp
